c: 6
v: 91
t: "They do not value God the way He should be valued when they say: ´God has not sent down anything to a human being.\" SAY: \"Who sent down the Book which Moses came with, as Light and guidance for mankind? You publish it on (separate) sheets to show it around, while you (also) hide a great deal [of it]. You have been taught what neither you yourselves nor your forefathers ever knew.\" SAY: \"God [has sent it];\" then leave them toying away with their speculation"